Create this directory structure (from the folder where site.yml lives):

mkdir -p roles/ccdc_dc2019/tasks
mkdir -p roles/ccdc_fileserver/tasks
mkdir -p roles/ccdc_web/tasks
mkdir -p roles/ccdc_db/tasks
mkdir -p roles/ccdc_mail/tasks
mkdir -p roles/ccdc_soc/tasks
mkdir -p roles/ccdc_workstation/tasks
mkdir -p roles/ccdc_kali_attacker/tasks

Then create the following tasks/main.yml files.
roles/ccdc_dc2019/tasks/main.yml
roles/ccdc_fileserver/tasks/main.yml
roles/ccdc_web/tasks/main.yml
roles/ccdc_db/tasks/main.yml
roles/ccdc_mail/tasks/main.yml
roles/ccdc_soc/tasks/main.yml
roles/ccdc_workstation/tasks/main.yml
roles/ccdc_kali_attacker/tasks/main.yml
